.. _tutorialspol:

Tutorials
=========

In this section, we will introduce the newly developed workflows that can be used in PySoftK_ for analysing polymers
and other soft-matter systems. Tutorials for a new set of functionalities like estimation of densities, detection of
ring-ring stacking enviorements, contact analysis have been developed.  

